data.description: Wonderful newer split bedroom layout home features a large kitchen with island, lots of windows in living and dining, gas fireplace and the TV above the fireplace is included. Note there are accordion blinds that have low light and blackout features. This home also boasts double vanity in guest bath. The backyard has a storage shed that is included, along with a nice covered patio. Great location that is close to everything from; the Nampa greenbelt, Neighborhood Market, Lake Lowell and the Marketplace for all your shopping needs. The sellers will also pay for the carpets to be cleaned upon closing. OPEN HOUSE SATURDAY 2/25/23 12p-3p. PRICE REDUCTION AND $8,000 TOWARDS RATE BUY DOWN.
